部判断 `this.config.isDisabled` 来决定是否执行视觉反馈和 `onClick`；`setDisabled
()` 仅负责切换 `isDisabled` 标志和 `disableInteractive()` / `setAlpha()`。\\n  `
``typescript\\n  // 示例修复思路\\n  target.on(\'pointerover\', () => {\\n    if
(this.config.isDisabled) return;\\n    killTweensOf(this.scene, this);\\n    ...
\\n  });\\n  // 构造函数中不再因 isDisabled 提前 return\\n  if (this.config.isDi
sabled) {\\n    target.disableInteractive();\\n    this.setAlpha(0.6);\\n  }\\n 
```\\n- **依据**: `docs/design-docs/ui-style-guide/03-component.md` 3.1 节要求「
